1
00:00:00,150 --> 00:00:01,160
Hi everyone.

2
00:00:01,170 --> 00:00:05,720
Thanks for sticking by and I hope you enjoy the course in this lesson.

3
00:00:05,730 --> 00:00:10,830
I would like to briefly clarify a source of confusion for many of our students.

4
00:00:10,840 --> 00:00:18,770
I'm sure that by this point you know that in order to start a function in Excel we need to type equals.

5
00:00:18,870 --> 00:00:25,310
However as we go ahead with the course you will sometimes see me start functions with plus.

6
00:00:25,320 --> 00:00:31,920
Please be aware that both symbols can be used interchangeably and it doesn't make any difference which

7
00:00:31,920 --> 00:00:33,360
of the two you go for.

8
00:00:33,360 --> 00:00:40,380
Just remember that every time when you type equals or plus in excel the program would understand that

9
00:00:40,470 --> 00:00:43,350
has a sign that you have started typing as a function.
